title: Bug 122584: Cascading parameter values cannot be displayed properly in HTML viewer
description: Description: Cascading parameter values cannot be displayed properly in HTML viewer.
OB: When viewing a design file in the HTML viewer, the cascading parameter values are not displayed correctly.
EB: The cascading parameter values should be displayed correctly in the HTML viewer.
SR:
To reproduce the issue: 
1. Open the attached design file in the HTML viewer. 
2. Click on the 'change parameter' button in the HTML viewer.
